---

<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-brand-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image / Visual -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-sm overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-700 to-brand-600">
          <!-- Placeholder for shop photo -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-16 h-16 text-warm-400/30 mx-auto" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5A2.25 2.25 0 0022.5 18.75V5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0020.25 3H3.75A2.25 2.25 0 001.5 5.25v13.5A2.25 2.25 0 003.75 21z" />
              </svg>
              <p class="text-warm-400/50 text-sm mt-2 font-heading tracking-wider">SHOP PHOTO</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Accent corner decoration -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -right-3 w-24 h-24 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-accent-500/30 rounded-sm"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-accent-500 mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-800 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white tracking-wider">
          About the Shop
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-warm-300 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            At Busted Knuckle Auto Repair and Painting, the name says it all. We're hands-on, old-school craftsmen who believe great work comes from getting your knuckles dirty and doing things right.
          </p>
          <p>
            Based in <strong class="text-warm-100">Lewiston, Idaho</strong>, we specialize in the kind of work that most shops won't touch: high-end custom paint jobs on classic cars, hot rods, and project builds. Every vehicle that rolls into our shop gets treated like it's our own.
          </p>
          <p>
            From ground-up restorations to head-turning custom paint, we combine traditional craftsmanship with modern techniques and materials. We're not the fastest shop in town &mdash; we're the shop that does it right the first time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats / Highlights -->
        <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading font-800 text-3xl text-accent-400">100%</div>
            <div class="text-warm-400 text-sm font-heading tracking-wider uppercase mt-1">Hands-On Work</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-heading font-800 text-3xl text-accent-400">Quality</div>
            <div class="text-warm-400 text-sm font-heading tracking-wider uppercase mt-1">Over Quantity</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
